    <a href="tel:+18554475023" class="nav-cta">Book a Call</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-left reveal-left">
    <p class="hero-tag">Rip It Labs</p>
    <h1>
      Automate<br>anything.<br>
      <span class="rilbots">RILbots.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      RILbots are fully custom AI agents built specifically for your business — not a platform you configure, not a subscription you manage. We design, build, and deploy an agent built entirely around the workflows you need automated.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="tel:+18554475023" class="btn-primary">Book a Strategy Call</a>
      <a href="#rilbots" class="btn-ghost">What Is a RILbot</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right reveal-right">
    <div class="hero-logo-wrap">
      <div class="hero-logo-glow"></div>
      <img class="hero-logo-img" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Rip It Labs">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat-item reveal">
    <div class="stat-num">100<span class="unit">%</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">Custom-built — no templates, no platforms, no shortcuts</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item reveal">
    <div class="stat-num">Custom</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Pricing — scoped to your operation, scaled to what you actually need</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item reveal">
    <div class="stat-num">Any</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Industry — if your business has workflows, we can automate them</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item reveal">
    <div class="stat-num">4</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Senior leaders directly involved in every client engagement</div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="rilbots-section" id="rilbots">
  <div class="rilbots-inner">
    <div class="reveal-left">
      <p class="label">Our Product</p>
      <div class="rilbots-name">RILbots</div>
      <div class="rilbots-sub">by Rip It Labs</div>
      <p class="rilbots-desc">A RILbot is a fully custom AI agent built specifically for your business — not a generic tool you configure, and not a SaaS product you subscribe to. We design, build, and deploy it from the ground up around the exact workflows you need automated.</p>
      <p class="rilbots-desc">Every RILbot is unique to the client it is built for. Your operations, your data, your rules — built into an intelligent agent that works the way your business works.</p>
      <a href="tel:+18554475023" class="btn-primary">Get Your RILbot</a>
    </div>
    <div class="rilbots-right reveal-right">
      <div class="rilbot-feature">
        <div class="feature-bullet"></div>
        <div><h4>Built for Your Workflows</h4><p>No two RILbots are the same. Every system is designed around the specific tasks, data, and processes that make your business run.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rilbot-feature">
        <div class="feature-bullet"></div>
        <div><h4>Integrates with What You Have</h4><p>RILbots connect directly to your existing software, CRMs, databases, and tools. No ripping out what already works.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rilbot-feature">
        <div class="feature-bullet"></div>
        <div><h4>Human Oversight at Every Step</h4><p>Your team stays in control. Every RILbot is built with clear checkpoints so humans make the calls that matter.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rilbot-feature">
        <div class="feature-bullet"></div>
        <div><h4>Scales with Your Business</h4><p>As your operations grow and change, your RILbot evolves with them. We stay involved well after initial deployment.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rilbot-feature">
        <div class="feature-bullet"></div>
        <div><h4>Secure and Compliant by Design</h4><p>Built with your compliance requirements and data security standards baked in from day one — not bolted on afterward.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mission-section" id="mission">
  <div class="mission-inner">
    <div class="reveal-left">
      <p class="label">Our Mission</p>
      <div class="mission-quote">To give every business access to <em>genuinely intelligent automation</em> — built honestly, deployed responsibly, and designed to last.</div>
      <p class="mission-body">AI has a credibility problem. Too many businesses have been sold dashboards they do not use, chatbots that do not help, and automation that breaks under real conditions. We started Rip It Labs because we believed there was a better way — one that starts with understanding the business first and builds technology second. RILbots are the result of that philosophy: agents that actually work, for businesses that actually need them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mission-pillars reveal">
      <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-label">Precision</div><p>We build tightly scoped solutions. Not platforms that do everything adequately — systems that do one thing exceptionally well for your specific operation.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-label">Transparency</div><p>You know what we are building, why, and how it works. No black boxes, no lock-in, no surprises on the invoice or after go-live.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-label">Accountability</div><p>Our senior team is on every project. If something is not working right, we are the ones who fix it — not a support queue.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-label">Human-First</div><p>AI handles the volume and the repetition. Your team keeps judgment and control. That is not a limitation — it is good design.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-section" id="services">
  <div class="services-header reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="label">What We Build</p>
      <h2>Everything your RILbot needs to work in the real world.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="services-desc">A complete RILbot deployment covers everything from initial research through ongoing support. Here is what goes into every engagement.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 01</span><h3>Custom AI Agent Design</h3><p>We design your RILbot from the ground up — scoped around your specific workflows, data sources, and operational requirements. No templates.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 02</span><h3>Workflow Automation</h3><p>End-to-end automation of repetitive, high-volume tasks — reducing manual work, cutting errors, and freeing your team for higher-value work.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 03</span><h3>Document & Data Processing</h3><p>Agents that extract, classify, and process large volumes of documents, forms, and data — accurately and at a scale that humans alone cannot match.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 04</span><h3>System Integration</h3><p>We connect your RILbot to your existing CRMs, databases, and business software. Your new AI works inside the tools your team already uses.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 05</span><h3>Compliance-Ready Infrastructure</h3><p>For regulated industries and data-sensitive operations, we build with your compliance requirements from the start — not as an afterthought.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">// 06</span><h3>Ongoing Research & Optimization</h3><p>After deployment, we keep testing and improving. Your RILbot gets better over time as we track performance and refine what is working.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="how-header reveal">
    <p class="label">How We Work</p>
    <h2>A clear process. No surprises.</h2>
    <p>Every RILbot is built the same way — deep discovery before a single line of code, followed by rigorous testing before anything goes live.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="how-steps">
    <div class="how-step reveal"><div class="step-num">01</div><h4>Discovery</h4><p>We start by learning your operation. We map your workflows, find what is actually slowing you down, and agree on a definition of success before anything else.</p></div>
    <div class="how-step reveal"><div class="step-num">02</div><h4>Design</h4><p>We design your RILbot architecture around your specific needs. You see the full plan and approve it before we build a single component.</p></div>
    <div class="how-step reveal"><div class="step-num">03</div><h4>Build & Test</h4><p>We build in iterations against real operational conditions — edge cases, failure modes, compliance requirements. Nothing ships until it is ready.</p></div>
    <div class="how-step reveal"><div class="step-num">04</div><h4>Deploy & Support</h4><p>Go-live is the start of the relationship, not the end of it. We stay involved after deployment to monitor, improve, and keep your RILbot working as your business evolves.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section" id="why">
  <div class="why-inner">
    <div class="why-left reveal-left">
      <p class="label">Why Rip It Labs</p>
      <h2>We build what you need. Not what's easiest to sell.</h2>
      <p class="why-body">Most AI vendors hand you a platform and call it a solution. We do the opposite — we spend time in your operations first, understand the real friction, and then build around it. No upsells, no vague roadmaps, no demos that do not reflect reality.</p>
      <a href="tel:+18554475023" class="btn-primary">Talk to Our Team</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="why-list">
      <li class="why-item reveal"><div class="why-dot"></div><div><div class="why-title">Fully Custom, Always</div><p class="why-desc">Every RILbot is built from scratch for the client it serves. There are no pre-built modules we are trying to fit your business into.</p></div></li>
      <li class="why-item reveal"><div class="why-dot"></div><div><div class="why-title">Research Before Code</div><p class="why-desc">We do not start building until we understand your operations deeply. That up-front investment means fewer problems after launch and systems people actually use.</p></div></li>
      <li class="why-item reveal"><div class="why-dot"></div><div><div class="why-title">Human Oversight Is Non-Negotiable</div><p class="why-desc">Every RILbot we deploy has clear human checkpoints built in. Your team never loses visibility or control over what the agent is doing.</p></div></li>
      <li class="why-item reveal"><div class="why-dot"></div><div><div class="why-title">Serious Scope Only</div><p class="why-desc">We focus on mid-size to enterprise operations where automation creates real, measurable impact — not small projects that will not move the needle.</p></div></li>
      <li class="why-item reveal"><div class="why-dot"></div><div><div class="why-title">Senior Team on Every Project</div><p class="why-desc">Our leadership is directly involved from the first call through final deployment. You are working with the people making the decisions, not a delivery team.</p></div></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="industries-section" id="industries">
  <div class="industries-top reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="label">Industries</p>
      <h2>If your business has workflows, we can automate them.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="industries-desc">RILbots have been built across a wide range of industries. We do not limit ourselves to specific sectors — if there is a repetitive, high-volume, or complex workflow in your operation, we can build an agent for it.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="industry-grid reveal">
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Insurance & Claims</div><div class="industry-note">Policy processing, claims intake, document review</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Real Estate</div><div class="industry-note">Lead management, contract processing, due diligence</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Legal Services</div><div class="industry-note">Document review, intake automation, research support</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Financial Services</div><div class="industry-note">Compliance workflows, reporting, client onboarding</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Auto & Transportation</div><div class="industry-note">Claims processing, fleet management, inspections</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Construction & Property</div><div class="industry-note">Project tracking, vendor management, permitting</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Healthcare Administration</div><div class="industry-note">Patient intake, billing, records management</div></div>
    <div class="industry-card"><div class="industry-name">Any Enterprise Operation</div><div class="industry-note">If you have workflows, we can build a RILbot for them</div></div>
  </div>
  <p class="industries-footer reveal">Do not see your industry? That just means we have not listed it yet. <a href="tel:+18554475023">Give us a call.</a></p>
</section>

<section class="team-section" id="team">
  <div class="team-header reveal">
    <p class="label">The Team</p>
    <h2>The people behind every RILbot.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Rip It Labs is run by a senior team of builders and researchers. Everyone here has done this work firsthand — there is no layer of project managers between you and the people actually building your system.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="team-grid">
    <div class="team-card reveal">
      <div class="team-photo">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Tim Cavin" class="has-src">
        <div class="team-initials">TC</div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-info">
        <div class="team-name">Tim Cavin</div>
        <div class="team-role">Chief Executive Officer</div>
        <p class="team-bio">Tim leads Rip It Labs — its direction, client strategy, and the standard every RILbot is held to. He stays directly involved across every major engagement and makes sure the business delivers what it promises.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-card reveal">
      <div class="team-photo">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Ms. Henke" class="has-src">
        <div class="team-initials">MH</div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-info">
        <div class="team-name">Ms. Henke</div>
        <div class="team-role">Vice President</div>
        <p class="team-bio">Ms. Henke runs operations, client relationships, and project delivery at Rip It Labs. She makes sure engagements stay on track and that clients always know exactly where their project stands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-card reveal">
      <div class="team-photo">
        <img src="data:image/webp;base64," alt="Niall Elbert" class="has-src">
        <div class="team-initials">NE</div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-info">
        <div class="team-name">Niall Elbert</div>
        <div class="team-role">Chief Technology Officer</div>
        <p class="team-bio">Niall designs the technical architecture behind every RILbot. He leads system design, integration work, and the engineering decisions that determine whether a deployment holds up under real conditions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-card reveal">
      <div class="team-photo">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Hannah Ellis" class="has-src">
        <div class="team-initials">HE</div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-info">
        <div class="team-name">Hannah Ellis</div>
        <div class="team-role">Chief Research Officer</div>
        <p class="team-bio">Hannah runs the research and validation layer behind everything we ship. She sets the testing standards, leads model evaluation, and decides whether a RILbot is genuinely ready for production — not just ready for a demo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section" id="contact">
  <h2>Ready to see what a <em>RILbot</em> can do for your business?</h2>
  <p class="cta-sub">Book a strategy call with our team. We will walk through your workflows, give you an honest read on what is possible, and show you exactly what we would build.</p>
  <div class="cta-actions">
    <a href="tel:+18554475023" class="btn-primary">Call: (855) 447-5023</a>
    <a href="mailto:ripitlabs@gmail.com" class="btn-ghost">Email Us</a>
  </div>
  <p class="cta-meta">No pitch deck. No pressure. Just a real conversation about your operations.</p>
</section>

